name: Landing page Busin 1
description:
Busin 1 is a pure multi-purpose PSD and Figma theme.


This is a landing page that will suit any of your lines of business. It is loaded with layers and is very easy to edit. You can edit and customize it to any of your needs, 10++ pages you need


Functions


- 10+ full layer Adobe Photoshop .PSD and Figma files

- Designed with responsiveness in mind

- Clean, modern design

- Well organized layers make it very easy to update

- All fonts used in templates are available in Google Font.
